  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5399537/" class="title-link">戊戌狂想曲</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5399537"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/leoyin1989/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1732691-64.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/leoyin1989/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">白鹇</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-04-22"
      class="main-meta">2012-04-22 14:19:21</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5399537_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  1 康有为的变法维新思想，据其自编年谱所说，并非是从甲午战败后才开始的，而是始于更早前的一次顿悟。那是1878年，他还在礼山草堂苦读经史时，一次打坐的过程中“忽见天地万物皆我一体，大放光明”，恍惚间，他觉得自己是孔子再世：“自以为圣人，则欣喜而笑，忽思苍生困苦，...

