  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2179134/" class="title-link">印刷质量很好，对得起价格</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2179134"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3134880/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3134880-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3134880/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">洗砚春秋</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-07-30"
      class="main-meta">2009-07-30 16:51:16</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2179134_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  茅海建的书，内容就不用评价了，应该都当得起精品二字。我是在卓越订货的，送过来封面略有灰渍，但总体而言很不错，入手沉甸甸的，印刷也不错，厚厚一本，对得起价格。一家之言，仅供欲购此书的书友参考。

